# Performance

- No feature without a performance budget.
- First paint must not wait on plugins, agents, terminal, LSP, git, debug, or network.
- No startup plugin activation; no star-activation equivalent.
- Lazy everything heavy; measure or stub measurement (label mocks clearly).
- Budgets: window under 300ms, shell under 500ms, palette under 50ms, terminal panel under 50ms.
